skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: brewery locator
des: Going to a new city and want to check out some local breweries? Just ask Brewery Locator to find you a brewery in the city! Brewery Locatory can give you a random brewery every time you ask for a brewery, or it will give you the top rated brewery if you ask for it!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
